node.contents: what is the difference between `-keep class org.spongycastle.** { *; }` and `-keep class org.spongycastle.**` ?

astNode.text: what is the difference between `-keep class org.spongycastle.** { *; }` and `-keep class org.spongycastle.**` ?

node.contents: -keep class org.spongycastle.** { *; } means keep all class name and class methods/fields in package and -keep class org.spongycastle.** means keep all class in package
